# `pseudo` is a dev-only pseudo-localization locale used by the extract
# workflow; the shipped app never imports its compiled catalog. `lingui
# compile` regenerates it, so keep the artifact out of the tree (the `en`/`ar`
# compiled catalogs the app imports are committed).
